  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill or grill pan to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together the tandoor spice blend, chilli flakes, garam masala, salt, black pepper, and lemon juice.",
    "Add the chicken breast to the bowl and toss to coat with the spice mixture.",
    "Thread the marinated chicken onto skewers, leaving a little space between each piece.",
    "Brush the grill or grill pan with olive oil to prevent sticking.",
    "Grill the kebabs for 10-12 minutes, turning occasionally, or until cooked through.",
    "Transfer the kebabs to a plate and brush with Greek yogurt.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve immediately."
  ],
